'''阿尔德門圣博托尔夫堂'''（St Botolph's Church, Aldgate, St Botolph-without-Aldgate）<ref>[http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=2Q8HAAAAQAAJ&pg=PA36&dq=%22Aldgate+church%22&lr=&as_brr=3&cd=12#v=onepage&q=%22Aldgate%20church%22&f=false]</ref> 是一座圣公会教堂，位于英国[[伦敦市|伦敦市]]的猎犬沟渠街（Houndsditch）与[[阿尔德門|阿尔德門大街]]（Aldgate High Street）路口。目前的砖砌建筑为18世纪建造，石头包边<ref>"The Old Churches of London" Cobb,G: London, Batsford, 1942</ref> 钟楼为正方形，尖顶为方尖碑形<ref name="Architecture">{{cite book| last = Saunders| first = Ann| title = The Art and Architecture of London: An Illustrated Guide| publisher = Phaidon| year = 1984 | location = Oxford| page= 80}}</ref>。 

